      "id": "PopularPost193214",
      "post_content": "Fires of Yavimaya is usually used as a combo card with Blastoderm and Saproling Burst. A turn one Birds of Paradise followed by a T2 Fires of Yavimaya allowed a T3 5/5 Shroud Haste via Blastoderm.  \nThis combo, if followed up by a T4 Saproling Burst, usually spelled doom to Standard players circa 2000-2001 season.  \nThis strategy was developed by Magic Hall Of Fame player Zvi Moshowitz.",
